<p>The 4th ASFAA Sport for All Training Course will be held in Macau, China. </p><p>The theme of this year is “Sports for All and Quality of Life of Citizens” – The course is designed to provide a structural and practical training to personnel involved or about to engage in the field of Sport for All. Participants that successfully complete the course will receive a certificate from ASFAA. </p><p>Participants are required to have a good command of English as this is the official course language. Simultaneous translation in English and Mandarin will be available in all training sessions.For more details, please check the dedicated website at:</p><p><a href="http://sport.gov.mo/en/calendary/type/item/id/6334" target="_blank" data-saferedirecturl="https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&q=http://sport.gov.mo/en/calendary/type/item/id/6334&source=gmail&ust=1505463124575000&usg=AFQjCNEV7jFlmIk06s5lxwH2-chDAT8F2w" style="color: rgb(17, 85, 204);">http://sport.gov.mo/en/calendary/type/item/id/6334</a></p>